    Z "{i}*risilla*{/i} Oye, pequeña."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:14
translate spanish vai_1_722b1b81:

    # Z "Wanted to surprise me, huh?"
    Z "¿Querías sorprenderme, eh?"

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:17
translate spanish vai_1_bb946a88:

    # A "Come, let's hop on the bed!"
    A "¡Ven, subámonos a la cama!"

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:23
translate spanish vai_2_7bd15845:

    # A "I know it's difficult... we don't really speak the language the same way it's written, too."
    A "Sé que es difícil... nosotros tampoco hablamos igual que escribimos."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:26
translate spanish vai_2_767eb08a:

    # Ka "Really? {i}*sigh*{/i} I miss home language very much..."
    Ka "¿De verdad? {i}*suspiro*{/i} Echo mucho de menos mi lengua materna..."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:27
translate spanish vai_2_8ab73088:

    # Ka "I will take a break for now, I think."
    Ka "Creo que tomaré un descanso por ahora."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:30
translate spanish vai_2_c3c46cf8:

    # Ka "Oh, it's [persistent.player_name]!"
    Ka "¡Oh, es [persistent.player_name]!"

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:31
translate spanish vai_2_5a7ab9f5:

    # Ka "You want to speak with [A], yes? I will leave."
    Ka "¿Quieres hablar con [A], verdad? Me retiraré."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:37
translate spanish vai_3_90b75bd7:

    # S "There's no way you're serious."
    S "Es imposible que hables en serio."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:38
translate spanish vai_3_714f35a6:

    # A "I'm not joking, sister..."
    A "No estoy bromeando, hermana..."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:41
translate spanish vai_3_7a97e4cd:

    # S "You're telling me you washed my sword with soap because it looked dirty."
    S "¿Me estás diciendo que lavaste mi espada con jabón porque parecía sucia?"

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:42
translate spanish vai_3_91ef1eca:

    # S "Have you ever heard of something called rust?"
    S "¿Has oído hablar de algo llamado óxido?"

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:45
translate spanish vai_3_471079e4:

    # A "Look, of course I knew. I mean... I didn't. But!"
    A "Mira, claro que lo sabía. Quiero decir... no lo sabía. ¡Pero...!"

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:48
translate spanish vai_3_018259f8:

    # S "Next time you're cleaning my room, please... {i}*sigh*{/i}"
    S "La próxima vez que limpies mi habitación, por favor... {i}*suspiro*{/i}"

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:49
translate spanish vai_3_8cdf3054:

    # S "[A], I appreciate it. Just stay away from... sharp things, okay?"
    S "[A], te lo agradezco. Solo mantente alejada de... cosas afiladas, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:50
translate spanish vai_3_4fa744aa:

    # S "Anyways, that's all I wanted to ask. [persistent.dad!c] is here for you. I'll see you later."
    S "En fin, eso es todo lo que quería preguntar. [persistent.dad!c] está aquí para ti. Nos vemos más tarde."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:56
translate spanish vai_4_34260237:

    # S "You know, sometimes I wonder... If we weren't sisters, would we be friends?"
    S "Sabes, a veces me pregunto... si no fuéramos hermanas, ¿seríamos amigas?"

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:59
translate spanish vai_4_2b0f0824:

    # A "That's a tough question. I think you're tolerable, for a big sis..."
    A "Esa es una pregunta difícil. Creo que eres tolerable, para ser la hermana mayor..."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:62
translate spanish vai_4_13409749:

    # S "Such high praise. I think you deserve extra rough brushing for that one."
    S "Qué gran elogio. Creo que mereces un cepillado extra fuerte por eso."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:66
translate spanish vai_4_4b30c007:

    # Z "Hey girls, don't worry, take your time. I'll come back in a few."
    Z "Oye, chicas, no os preocupéis, tomaos vuestro tiempo. Volveré en un rato."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:72
translate spanish vai_5_1f926a0e:

    # A "Thanks, [S], I owe you one. My hair has been all fuzzy today."
    A "Gracias, [S], te debo una. Hoy he tenido el pelo todo encrespado."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:75
translate spanish vai_5_f0786c15:

    # S "I was always a bit jealous of my little sister's hair... but me, and pigtails just wouldn't work."
    S "Siempre he tenido un poco de envidia del pelo de mi hermanita... pero a mí las coletas no me quedarían bien."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:79
translate spanish vai_5_08ec795b:

    # Z "Hey girls... [A], got a few minutes? You can finish up first, I'll be back."
    Z "Oye, chicas... [A], ¿tienes unos minutos? Termina primero, yo vuelvo enseguida."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:85
translate spanish vai_6_f24443b5:

    # W "...that's not bad, either. By the gods... my little Queen of a [persistent.da] is all grown up now."
    W "...tampoco está mal. Por los dioses... mi pequeña Reina de [persistent.da] ya ha crecido."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:88
translate spanish vai_6_da3dc4c8:

    # A "I don't know, [persistent.mom]... it kind of makes me look old."
    A "No lo sé, [persistent.mom]... hace que parezca mayor."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:91
translate spanish vai_6_714ee34e:

    # W "Not at all... with a body like that underneath, you will have men drooling in anticipation."
    W "En absoluto... con un cuerpo así debajo, tendrás a los hombres babeando de ganas."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:97
translate spanish vai_7_8875a815:

    # W "Mh... I just had to see it again. And next time, I might just devour you instead."
    W "Mh... tenía que verlo otra vez. Y la próxima vez, quizá simplemente te devore."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:100
translate spanish vai_7_463b12fa:

    # W "You do look like one tasty meal. {i}*sigh*{/i} I am one proud [persistent.mom], today."
    W "De verdad pareces un plato delicioso. {i}*suspiro*{/i} Hoy me siento muy orgullosa de ser una [persistent.mom]."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:108
translate spanish vai_bridge_9c4d5012:

    # A "What's up, [persistent.dad]!"
    A "¡Qué pasa, [persistent.dad]!"

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:117
translate spanish vsi_1_98e673e6:

    # S "Have you seen how that boy in the city stared at you?"
    S "¿Has visto cómo te miraba ese chico en la ciudad?"

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:120
translate spanish vsi_1_4fd7cc69:

    # A "Yeah... so young though. Around my age, if not younger?"
    A "Sí... aunque era bastante joven. De mi edad, si no más joven."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:121
translate spanish vsi_1_a8c8b7f2:

    # A "I think the look I gave him scared him off, though."
    A "Aunque creo que la mirada que le lancé lo asustó."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:124
translate spanish vsi_1_20f7dd48:

    # S "{i}*chuckles*{/i} You gave him the stare of death."
    S "{i}*risilla*{/i} Le diste la mirada de la muerte."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:127
translate spanish vsi_1_2babe7cb:

    # S "Anyways, want to hang outside later? After dinner, I mean."
    S "En fin, ¿quieres que salgamos luego? Después de cenar, quiero decir."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:130
translate spanish vsi_1_7bd4c06e:

    # A "Yup, why not! See you later!"
    A "¡Claro, por qué no! ¡Nos vemos luego!"

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:137
translate spanish vsi_2_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/interactions.rpy:138
